  },
  "quizPhishingQ4Explain": "Spear-phishing is a personalized attack: the attacker researches the victim (job title, colleagues, projects) and crafts a convincing message. Its success rate is 10x higher than mass phishing.",
  "@quizPhishingQ4Explain": {
